","html":"<div class="rd3-page">
    <header class="header" style="background-image: url('/apps/molgenis-viz/img/home-header.jpg');">
        <div class="content">
            <h1>MOLGENIS-RD3</h1>
            <p>The Rare Disease Database</p>
            </br>
            <h1>Data providers</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-filter" />
    </header>
    <div class="section bg-gray-050">
        <div class="section-content">
            <h2 id="section-intro-title">Data providers</h2>
            <p>Every data provider has their own <i>staging area</i>, this private space is where providers can view and modify the records that they have submitted. Please find your staging area in the list below. Ensure that you have a MOLGENIS account and that you have access to your staging area. For more information about the data submission process please find the manual <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ms7ZtsbFwRjUknnuZ6S969rVi23_P4fO-t2h_Z4Sysc/edit?usp=sharing">here</a>.</p>
            <h2>List of data providers</h2>
            <p>Please log in before going to your staging area.</p>
            <div class="d-flex" style="gap: 1em">
              <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">UMCG</h5>
                  <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Go to UMCG's staging area</a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">SRUMC</h5>
                  <a href="https://erdera.molgeniscloud.org/Staging%20area%20SRUMC" class="btn btn-primary">Go to SRUMC's staging area</a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">TUM</h5>
                  <a href="https://erdera.molgeniscloud.org/Staging%20area%20TUM/pages/#/Home" class="btn btn-primary">Go to SRUMC's staging area</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section bg-gray-000">
        <div class="section-content">
            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p class="text-center">Please contact us if you have any questions about RD3 or need help with the submission process</p>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="mailto:support@molgenis.org">Email us</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>","javascript":"","dependencies":{"css":[],"javascript":[]}}
